/kind bug What steps did you take and what happened: from google.cloud import logging_v2 results in ImportError: cannot import name 'logging_v2' only in Jupyter Notebook. Anything else you would like to add: This error came in when importing fairing from kubeflow Environment:
Kubeflow version: build version dev_local kfctl version: (use kfctl version): v1.0.2-0-ga476281 Kubernetes platform: GKE Kubernetes version: (use kubectl version): Client v1.17.2, Server v1.14.10-gke.40 OS (e.g. from /etc/os-release): Ubuntu 18.04
